de.affect.appraisal

Class AppraisalVariables

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.affect.appraisal.AppraisalVariables

  • public class AppraisalVariables
extends java.lang.Object
    The class AppraisalVariables holds all posssible variables and their values, which are the result of an subjective appraisal. Based on these values emotions will be generated.
